Species group: This is an inventory of the cumulative top 50 species at each of my focal sites in three focal regions (Massachussets, Maryland, Georgia).
Species must be among the top 50 at one site to be included on the list - but then the ranking at each site is also shown.
To be included in our species-level analysis, species/group must have max size > 15mm (size), be external feeder (habit), forest associated (habitat), feed on trees (host), phenology?
